<!DOCTYPE html>
html(lang="en")
	head
		meta(charset="UTF-8")
		link(rel="stylesheet", href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css", integrity="sha384-TX8t27EcRE3e/ihU7zmQxVncDAy5uIKz4rEkgIXeMed4M0jlfIDPvg6uqKI2xXr2", crossorigin="anonymous")
		link(rel="preconnect", href="https://fonts.gstatic.com")
		link(rel="stylesheet", href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto&display=swap")
		link(rel="stylesheet", href="/static/stylesheets/style.css")
		link(rel="icon", type="imagem/png", href="/static/images/favicon.png") 
		title Aposentadoria Ativa
		script(src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ho+j7jyWK8fNQe+A12Hb8AhRq26LrZ/JpcUGGOn+Y7RsweNrtN/tE3MoK7ZeZDyx" crossorigin="anonymous")
	body

		div(class="container-md")
			div(class="container-md text-center")
				img(src="/static/images/logo.png" class="img-fluid" id="logo" alt="Logo")
			
			div(class="container-md")
				form(action="/register" method="POST")
					div(class="form-group")
						label(for="name") Nome:
						br
						input(type="text", class="form-control", name="name")
						br
			
					div(class="form-group")
						label(for="datanascimento") Data de Nascimento:
						br
						input(type="date", class="form-control", name="datanascimento", id="datanascimento")
						br
					
					div(class="form-group")
						label(for="email") Email:
						br
						input(type="email", class="form-control", name="email", id="email")
						br


					div(class="form-group")
						label(for="cep") CEP:
						br
						input(type="text", class="form-control", name="cep", id="cep")
						br

					div(class="form-group")
						label(for="senha") Senha:
						br
						input(type="password", class="form-control",name="senha", id="senha")
						small(id="passwordHelpBlock", class="form-text text-muted") Sua senha precisa ter entre 8 e 20 caracteres. Ela precisa, também, conter letras e números. Por favor, não coloque seu nome, ou sua data de nascimento!

					button(type="submit", class="btn btn-lg btn-block " id="btn-purple") Concluir cadastro
			
			